        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cobleskill_(village)%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Cobleskill’s 1900 railroad station, still owned by the Delaware & Hudson, anchors the village’s historic core.",
